<function>

access:  static public

name: config

param: string, $group

param: string, $elem, NULL

return: mixed

</function>

Safely gets a configuration group array or element value.

* Parameters:

 * string //$group//: The name of the group.

 * string //$elem//: The name of the element in the group.

* Returns mixed: The value of the configuration group or element.